citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:20pmon March
30, 2023. Contact was attempted by knocking on doors to the house and kennel, beeped the car horn and waited for 30
minutes. No contact was able to be made.
End Section
